Just a guess : may be you've got the wrong MTU : 1524 for me (PPP/Modem,
not PPP/ISDN) and the pinging adjusts that.
What kernel release are you using, did you obtain the ISDN sources from
ftp.suse.com, which ppp release, which modutils ?
